| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-4590 — Recovery Inhibition (spacebears)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 8ea818f7-0c3f-5205-8e81-435d3a7cdcbf"
